            "scent_heading": "Patchouli & Cedarwood",
            "heading-position": false,
            "scent_details": "<p> <b class=\"value\"> Refreshing &amp; Relaxing\n <b></b> </b></p> A captivating, rich bouquet of warm woody notes of red cedar and amyris perfectly complemented by the distinctive, earthy and sweet tones of patchouli. The Intense lemony aroma of May Chang adds a sparkling, fresh, sherbet-like twist to this moth-deterring blend.",
            "infoHeading": "Note Information",
            "infoDetails": "<p class=\"value-bold blue-text\">Top Notes</p><p>\n</p><li>Fresh, juicy May Chang reminds us of a joyful lemon sorbet<p></p>\n<p class=\"value-bold blue-text\">Middle Notes</p>\n<p> </p>\n</li>\n<li> Sweet Palmarosa is grassy and earthy getting us in the mood for a spring walk<p></p>\n<p class=\"value-bold blue-text\">Base Notes</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Red Cedarwood is the star of this concentrate, as its sweet, balsamic scent has the ability to cover the smell of keratin, which moths love!</li>\n<li>Deep and distinctive, herbaceous Patchouli gives this concentrate its rich, woody and slightly sweet aroma</li>\n</ul>\n</li>"
          }
        },
        "image_CkRFVB": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "width": "w-80",
