            "mimage": "shopify://shop_images/Group_1_800x_png.png",
            "scent_heading": "Lemon & Marjoram",
            "heading-position": false,
            "scent_details": "<p> <b class=\"value-bold\"> Zingy &amp; Zesty </b> </p>\nA spray of this exclusive scent will transport you to a fresh Mediterranean kitchen, with notes of lush greens, sweet, woody marjoram and vibrant lemon, it’s the perfect welcome to Spring.",
            "infoHeading": "Note Information",
            "infoDetails": "<p class=\"value-bold blue-text\">Top Notes</p><p>\n\n</p><li>Fresh and citrusy lemon has us feeling uplifted and ready for spring<p></p>\n<p class=\"value-bold blue-text\">Middle Notes</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>Sweet marjoram adds warm, delicately floral notes</li>\n<li>\nClary sage is distinctive and sweet, with herbaceous and earthy hints \n</li>\n<li>Palmarosa adds sweetness, as well as grassy and earthy undertones</li>\n</ul>\n</li>"
